title: Elliptical Machine | Rolling Hills Low Impact Workout | Fitscope Studio
description:
Elliptical Machine | Rolling Hills Low Impact Workout | Fitscope Studio

Join Meghan for this rolling hills elliptical machine interval workout. Making use of both resistance and inclines, this workout simulates going up and down rolling hills to  pop soundtrack. Great low impact cardio and strength workout.

Class plan: 
5 min warmup 
23 min rolling hills 
2 min cool down
